ne;">Julian Schillinger</a><span>. The trio solved the ancient problem of t=
he Herculaneum Papyri, a library of scrolls that were flash-fried by the er=
uption of Mount Vesuvius in 79 AD. The scrolls, or a portion of them, are n=
